description:
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency: Table storing synchronization signal frequency information for GUtran cells.

dateTime: Timestamp of the data record.
Area_Name: Name of the geographical area.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  Unknown identifier (likely redundant).
Id4:  Combination of ARFCN and SCS.
vsDataType: Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency.userLabel: User-defined label (currently empty).
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency.smtcOffset: Offset of the SMTC (Synchronization Message Transmission Cycle).
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency.smtcDuration: Duration of the SMTC.
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency.gscn: Global Cell ID.
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency.smtcScs: Secondary Synchronization Channel (SCS) spacing.
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency.reservedBy:  Reserved by information, containing various identifiers.
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency.bandList: List of supported frequency bands.
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency.band:  Frequency band.
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency.smtcPeriodicity: Periodicity of the SMTC.
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency.arfcn: Absolute Radio Frequency Channel Number.
GUtranSyncSignalFrequency.gUtranSyncSignalFrequencyId: Unique identifier for the synchronization signal frequency.
